OL,3,CFarm partnership fined #80,000 after
OL,4,Cworker killed by exploding tyre
OL,6,FA Lancashire farm partnership has been
OL,7,Ffined #80,000 after a man died when a
OL,8,Ftractor tyre exploded at a dairy farm.
OL,10,FJoshua Hardman, 23, from Longridge,
OL,11,Fsuffered traumatic head injuries after
OL,12,Fthe incident in Hutton, near Preston,
OL,13,Fand died a month later.
OL,15,FIn a statement his family said he had
OL,16,Fa "heart of gold" and was an "amazing
OL,17,Fdad to his five-year-old daughter".
