OL,3,CFarm partnership fined #80,000 after
OL,4,Cworker killed by exploding tyre
OL,6,FJoshua had been helping inflate the
OL,7,Ftyre in May 2021 at the farm in
OL,8,FHutton, near Preston, run by W.
OL,9,FHesketh and Sons.
OL,11,FHe was nearby when the inner tube
OL,12,Fexploded propelling the wheel rim into
OL,13,Fhim.
OL,15,FAfter an investigation by the Health
OL,16,Fand Safety Executive (HSE), the farm
OL,17,Fpartnership pleaded guilty to a breach
OL,18,Fof the Health and Safety At Work Act.
