OL,4,Cworker killed by exploding tyre
OL,6,FFollowing the hearing at Preston
OL,7,Fmagistrates court, HSE inspector
OL,8,FAnthony Banks, said: "This was a
OL,9,Ftragic incident, and a much-loved
OL,10,Fyoung man has lost his life. It could
OL,11,Fhave easily been avoided with the
OL,12,Fright controls in place."
